WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.066 --> 00:00:05.366
Grandma, why are you here?

2
00:00:05.366 --> 00:00:06.633
Grandma is getting old

3
00:00:06.733 --> 00:00:08.133
Confused

4
00:00:08.133 --> 00:00:09.633
No memory

5
00:00:09.666 --> 00:00:12.166
I forgot that today is your birthday

6
00:00:12.166 --> 00:00:15.366
You see, this is what grandma specially prepared for you

7
00:00:15.366 --> 00:00:16.600
Thanks grandma

8
00:00:23.733 --> 00:00:28.433
Classmate, it's your birthday today. What's the matter?

9
00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:36.300
You're a trash picker

10
00:00:36.300 --> 00:00:38.600
You deserve the same birthday as me.

11
00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:41.400
It's us, Brother Chen, who is the first guardian of Jiangcheng

12
00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:42.400
Son of Strength

13
00:00:42.400 --> 00:00:43.766
Just like you

14
00:00:43.766 --> 00:00:47.533
Assisting wonderful poor ghosts who can afford to go to school with extreme poverty

15
00:00:47.533 --> 00:00:50.600
It is also worthy of the same birthday as our brother Chen.

16
00:00:51.866 --> 00:00:53.300
Why does this smell sour?

17
00:00:53.566 --> 00:00:56.600
Could it be that he didn't take a shower after picking up the trash?

18
00:00:56.733 --> 00:00:58.000
Who says no?

19
00:00:58.000 --> 00:00:59.400
Just this poor guy.

20
00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:00.933
Every time he doesn't go to class

21
00:01:00.933 --> 00:01:02.566
Just go to the trash and pick up the bottle

22
00:01:02.766 --> 00:01:05.533
He's dirty in the trash

23
00:01:05.533 --> 00:01:09.000
Maybe it's all viruses and bacteria or something

